data.description: Charming one story home with many updates! Premium location with no neighbors on one side or directly behind, plus it is walking distance to the community pool. This 3 bedroom home offers open-concept living, high ceilings, new cabinetry throughout, fresh interior & exterior paint, upgraded stainless steel appliances, new roof, new water heater, new AC, upgraded fixtures & more. Upon entering is a flex room that would make a great formal dining room, living room or home office. The kitchen has a breakfast bar that overlooks the dining & family rooms - both rooms have built-ins. Wall of windows along the family & dining rooms provide abundant natural light (these windows are new). Wood burning fireplace. Primary suite with dual vanities, a soaking tub, separate shower & walk-in closet. Great backyard with two tiled patios, additional concrete pad, storage shed, mature trees & tons of privacy. Ideally located minutes from I 10, the Energy Corridor, shopping & restaurants.
